  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "Hardhat provides the `evm_setAutomine` call which is very convenient to programmatically change the status of the automine mode, but I can't find a call to get the current status (e.g. `evm_getAutomine`). This would be very convenient for some usecases (e.g. I need to make sure automine is disabled at some point to perform some actions, but I want to restore automine to its previous status after I'm done).\r\n\r\nIs there such a call or would it be hard to implement?",
